title: Play On: Tootie's February 2017 Mix
description:
Hey, I gained a week. You know the drill by now: pretend this came out on February 1st. This mix notably contains many pop hits from the 80s, mostly by artists never before heard on a Tootie mix. Don't think too hard about the subliminal messages about this one. Would I lie to you?

All tracks are sourced from lossless material unless noted. All of the compilations' songs utilize playback gain values from Tootie's personal volume-leveling procedure, resulting in a consistent overall listening experience without the need to adjust the volume between songs. The method focuses on vocal volume.

Details:
Format: FLAC, level 7
Length: 1:22:15.243
Average bitrate: 823 kbps
Embedded CUE Sheet

Playback verified with foobar2000. Track notes embedded via comment fields and can be accessed with foobar2000. Track CTRB content ratings also included.
